'''Palpatine Causeway''' was a causeway in or near the [[Palace District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] as of [[6 ABY/Legends|6 ABY]]. It was doubtless named after [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="FC">''[[Star Wars: Force Commander]]''</ref>

